{{ else }}
To authenticate, please use the following One Time Password (OTP) from {{ .Tenant }}:
{{ end }}

{{ .RegistrationCode }}

Your OTP will be valid for {{ .ExpiresInMinutes }} minutes.
Do not share this OTP with anyone. {{ .Tenant }} takes your account security very seriously.{{ if $renderAsVerification }}

If you did not initiate this request, please ignore this email and contact support@lifenetwork.ai.{{ end }}

